{"tid":2463280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇拜登將中國枱舉到係美國既競爭對手？","createTime":"2021-03-26T14:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T14:44:05.000Z","uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a30015c77d7e1271ac05f5e79b6d5ed08bb05a3","tid":2463280,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:44:05.000Z","msg":"拜登表示，他已經明確對習近平說，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">美國並非要對抗中國，而是要跟中國進行激烈的競爭</span></span>，而且他公開要求中國要遵守國際規則，進行公平競爭。<br />\n「中國有一個總體目標&hellip;&hellip;成為世界領先、最富有、最強大的國家，」拜登對記者說。「在我的任期內，這不會發生，因為美國將繼續變強。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-56534030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-56534030&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=56ae667d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-56534030&h=cd0b77eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-56534030</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}